---
title: Rogan Josh Style Beef with chilli and crispy potatoes
description: Rogan josh is a signature recipe in Kashmiri cuisine. Our twist on this delicious dish features spiced beef and lentils topped with crispy roasted potatoes and a generous dollop of refreshing yoghurt.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF190828_R04_W41_UK_R3130-1_Main_red_chilli_high-72285ee8.jpg
